00:42:06.896 --> 00:42:10.696
What the problem with Qualtrics? Well, it shows up, and it says, "Click here." And

736
00:42:10.756 --> 00:42:14.616
we're all now embedded, "Don't click here," right?

737
00:42:15.396 --> 00:42:19.176
You're going to get in trouble. And if you think about it, I've reflected on my

738
00:42:19.216 --> 00:42:22.276
own. My own mailbox is not very full anymore,

739
00:42:23.156 --> 00:42:25.656
but my email inbox and my

740
00:42:26.496 --> 00:42:28.696
text inbox is filled with crap.

741
00:42:29.716 --> 00:42:32.016
And so it's noise, right? So people just ignore it.

742
00:42:32.076 --> 00:42:36.036
So I've never thought we'd see it circle all the way

743
00:42:36.136 --> 00:42:39.436
back, but now we're going back to paper. And it's not an age thing.

744
00:42:39.516 --> 00:42:43.016
There are old people that love digital,

