00:42:46.976 --> 00:42:48.756
contact me by paper." So

747
00:42:49.576 --> 00:42:51.276
the only challenge is now you have to

748
00:42:52.336 --> 00:42:54.556
maintain multimodality, which is a lot of work.

749
00:42:54.656 --> 00:42:55.356
Right. Yeah, yeah.

750
00:42:55.736 --> 00:42:59.356
I will say a not NCI funded cohort at

